# .gitignore — Autonomous AI Agent Team Workspace

# ─── Secrets & credentials ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
*.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# OpenClaw runtime state (personal, machine-specific)
.openclaw/
openclaw.json

# ─── Agent runtime state (personal, never shared) ──────────────────────────
# Daily memory logs are personal runtime state — exclude from commits
agents/*/memory/*.md
agents/*/memory/

# ─── Intel runtime outputs (research outputs, local only) ──────────────────
intel/DAILY-INTEL.md
intel/data/*.json
intel/data/*.jsonl
intel/data/*.tmp
intel/TOKEN-AUDIT-*.md
!intel/data/README.md

# ─── Daily memory logs (local context, stays on your machine) ──────────────
# These are created fresh each day by agents — personal context files
memory/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9].md

# ─── Private project workspaces (keep local) ─────────────────────────────
# Hackathon/private projects should go in projects/ and stay local
projects/

# ─── OS files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ─── Temp/build files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.tmp
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# ─── Editor ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ─── Local quarantine during cleanup ───────────────────────────────────────
_trash/

# ─── Optional local private helpers ─────────────────────────────────────────
scripts/hackathon-kickoff.sh
scripts/hackathon-status.sh

# ─── NOTE: The following are NOW tracked (template versions only):
# USER.md      → tracked as fill-in-blank template
# IDENTITY.md  → tracked as fill-in-blank template
# MEMORY.md    → tracked as fill-in-blank template
# TOOLS.md     → tracked as fill-in-blank template
# HEARTBEAT.md → tracked as fill-in-blank template
always-on-memory-agent/
